      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2615 - Rifa’ah ibn Musa asked Imam (as) about a Muhrim wearing socks (jawrabayn).\nImam (as) said: \"Yes, and also leather slippers (khuffayn) if he is compelled to wear them.\""
